title: ISIS cites Prophet 'insult' for Kabul Gurdwara attack; India grants priority visas to Sikhs, Hindus
description: The ISIS claimed responsibility for an attack on a Gurdwara in Afghanistan, saying it was retaliation for 'insults' to Prophet Mohammed. In a message posted on its propaganda site, ISIS said Saturday's attack targeted Hindus and Sikhs and the "apostates" who protected them in "an act of support for the Messenger of Allah". After the attack, Indian govt has decided to grant e-emergency visas to over 100 Afghan Sikhs and Hindus on priority. On Saturday, two people died while 7 were injured in the Kabul Gurdwara attack. title: Neeraj Chopra does India proud again; Clinches gold in Finland despite nasty fall
description: Olympic champion Neeraj Chopra won a gold medal at the Kuortane Games in Finland. He registered the win after throwing 86.69m on his first attempt. However, due to rain, Chopra had a nasty fall while making his third throw, after which he didn't throw but that first throw was enough for gold for Neeraj. The Athletics Federation of India has also allayed fears saying that Neeraj Chopra is fine after a bad slip. Watch this video to know more.|#NeerajChopra #KuortaneGames #GoldenBoy #GoldMedal #Finland #India #Javelin #JavelinThrow

Two years later, precisely in 1954, PSSI joined the Asian Football Confederation (AFC).|Since escaping from FIFA sanctions imposed in 2015, PSSI is now rising and starting to fix Indonesian football through tons of innovations. In 2016, PSSI woke up from adversity and continued to train to get up. The quality development and capacity building of Indonesian football's human resources have continued to be boosted, ranging from the number of young players, coaches, referees to other football management practitioners.|In 2017, PSSI also began to awaken women's soccer from sleep and continue to develop it. On 24 October 2019, Indonesia was officially chosen to host the 2021 FIFA U-20 World Cup. It was officially announced by the President of FIFA, Mr. Gianni Infantino in Shanghai, China. title: India's Russian coal imports jump 6-fold in 20 days; Gets 30% bumper discount | Report
description: As per Reuters report, there has been a steep spike in India's purchase of Russian coal as traders are getting offered 30% discount. The report states that the increase in trade comes despite western sanctions on Moscow for its invasion of Ukraine. Citing unpublished Indian government data, Reuters claimed that India's coal purchases jumped more than six-fold in the 20 days through Wednesday from the same period a year earlier to $331.17 million. Indian buyers are lapping up huge quantities of Russian coal despite high freight costs as European buyers shunned Russian coal.|#india   #russia #coal #globaltrade #oil #reuters #discount #moscow #delhi #coal

Mix together well with your hands. Scoop out 1-tablespoon portions and roll them into balls with your hands. Place the meatballs onto parchment-lined baking sheets and put the baking sheets in the freezer for 5 to 10 minutes for the meatballs to firm up.|To brown the meatballs, heat the olive oil in a heavy pot or large skillet over medium-high heat. Add the meatballs in batches, making sure not to overcrowd the pot. Cook, turning the meatballs to make sure they brown all over, 5 to 7 minutes per batch. Drain on paper towels.|Freezer instructions: Put the cooked meatballs in a single layer on baking sheets and put into the freezer. title: Menakar Peluang Ganjar di Pilpres 2024
description: Partai Nasdem mengumumkan tiga nama bakal calon presiden, yang potensial diusung oleh Nasdem pada Pilpres 2024. Salah-satunya, Kader partai lain yaitu PDI Perjuangan. Nama Ganjar Pranowo, politikus yang masuk jajaran tokoh dengan elektabilitas tertinggi di berbagai survei, kini mencuat di dua partai. Apa langkah selanjutnya, dari Nasdem dan PDIP? Seberapa besar peluang Ganjar dari kacamata partai politik? Eva Yunizar mengulasnya dalam dialog bersama Wasekjen PDI Perjuangan, Arif Wibowo, Ketua DPP Partai NasDem, Willy Aditya, Direktur Eksekutif IndoStrategic, Khoirul Umam

title: Ganjar Respons Namanya Diusulkan Capres 2024 oleh Nasdem, Ini Katanya..
description: SOLO, KOMPAS TV  Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo respons namanya diusulkan menjadi calon presiden atau Capres oleh Partai Nasdem.||||Hal tersebut disampaikan oleh Ganjar kala menghadiri Car Free Day di Kota Solo, Minggu (19/6).||||Ganjar menyampaikan bahwa perihal pencalonan presiden, dirinya akan ikut keputusan Ketua Umum PDIP Megawati Soekarnoputri.||||Baca Juga Usung Anies, Ganjar & Andika sebagai Kandidat Capres, Kaderisasi NasDem Gagal? di https://www.kompas.tv/article/300508/usung-anies-ganjar-andika-sebagai-kandidat-capres-kaderisasi-nasdem-gagal||||"Jelas berkali-kali, itu Bu Mega(wati)," ucap Ganjar ketika ditanya soal namanya diusulkan Capres oleh Nasdem.||||Dirinya mengaku masih menjadi kader PDIP, yang manut dengan keputusan partai.||||"Apa lagi? Aku PDI kok," ucap Ganjar pada wartawan.||||Sebelumnya, Ketua Umum Partai Nasdem Surya Paloh umumkan usulan tiga nama sebagai bakal calon presiden dalam Pilpres 2024.||||Surya Paloh telah mengumumkan tiga calon presiden (capres) yang akan diusung. Dalam keterangannya, tiga nama tersebut akan dipilih satu nama yang akan dicalonkan partai Nasdem sebagai Capres 2024.||||Tiga nama tersebut yakni Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan, Panglima TNI Andika Perkasa dan Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300518/ganjar-respons-namanya-diusulkan-capres-2024-oleh-nasdem-ini-katanya

title: As Europe wilts under the sun the heatwave sees temperature reach 40C in Spain | ITV News
description: People flocked to parks and pools across Europe for a bit of respite from the early heat wave that saw the mercury rise above 40C in France and Spain.|A blanket of hot air stretching from the Mediterranean to the North Sea is bringing much of Western Europe its first heat wave of the summer. |Meteorologists say the weather is a sign of what's to come as global warming continues, moving up in the calendar the temperatures that Europe would previously have seen only in July and August.|In France, some 18 million people woke to heat wave alerts affecting about a third of the country Friday.|Forest fire warnings were issued from the Pyrenees in the south to the Paris region.|Parisians and tourists were seeking shade and some even jumped into the Trocadero fountain to cool off on Saturday.|â€¢ Subscribe to ITV News on YouTube: http://bit.ly/2lOHmNj ||â€¢ Get breaking news and more stories at http://www.itv.com/news||||Follow ITV News on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/itvnews/ ||Follow ITV News on Twitter: https://twitter.com/itvnews ||Follow ITV News on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/itvnews/

title: Do Mechanical Keyboards Make You Better?
description: When it comes to the world of PC peripherals there is nothing more coveted, mythologized, or consuming than mechanical keyboards.|Itâ€™s become so deep that if you don't have one yourself, you are led to believe that youâ€™re missing out. But there is nothing more personalized and customizable than your keyboard. |Now that also means that the mechanical keyboard community can also be one of the most fanatical. |Since there is basically no ceiling for how unique your keyboard can be, you can fall down a rabbit hole that could end up costing you a pretty penny.|That being said, it is pretty incredible how far keyboard tech has come in the last ten years. Ukraine claims it has shot down a Russian Su-25 fighter jet in the Donetsk region. Zelensky announced that Russia has freed celebrated Ukrainian medic Yuliya Payevska. title: No to NATO, but Putin okay with Ukraine joining EU; Zelensky lauds backing by Brussels
description: Volodymr Zelensky hailed Brussels' support for Ukraine's European Union bid as a historic achievement. Brussels spearheaded a powerful show of European solidarity on Friday by backing Kyiv's bid for EU candidate status. "Now we are one step away from the beginning of a full-fledged integration with the European Union. We have a positive conclusion from the European Commission on the candidacy for Ukraine. This is a historical achievement for all who work for our state. The only thing left is to wait for the decision of the European Council next week," said Zelensky. Meanwhile, Russian President Vladimir Putin said he had "nothing against" Ukraine joining the EU. Watch the full video for more.|#ukraine #russia #zelensky #putin #nato #europeanunion

title: Air Force Ones Meet - A Day at Geneva Airport + Flight to Mont Blanc
description: I spent a day behind the scenes on the ramp at Geneva Airport. Sitting inside the push-back tug pushing 360 Tons Emirates B777-300/ER. Could this be the best airport job?|Then, I visited the new observation deck. Geneva airport host a wide array of airplane activities from general aviation to business jets to commercial airlines and VIP head of state airplane. In May 2021, both U.S. Air Force One (B747) and Russia Air Force One (IL-96) visited Geneva Airport. This video captured some of the interesting traffic visit to Geneva.|After that, I took off on a sightseeing flight from Geneva to Mont Blanc. Our Piper PA-46 Malibu departed Geneva towards Lake Geneva and the Alps. Within 20 minutes, we reached Mont Blanc. It was really spectacular flying over the Alps.

title: Israel bombards Hamas in Gaza after rocket attack amid soaring Israeli-Palestinian tensions
description: Israeli warplanes hit Hamas military sites in the Gaza Strip on Saturday in retaliation for rocket fire from the Palestinian enclave run by the Islamist movement, the Israeli army said. Earlier in the day, Palestinian militants fired a rocket into southern Israel shattering a two-month lull in violence at the Gaza-Israel border in contrast to soaring tensions in the occupied West Bank. The Hamas-controlled Gaza coastal enclave of 2.3 million people has been under an Israeli blockade since 2007. title: Singaporeâ€™s BIGGEST Street Food!! 5 Things You HAVE TO EAT at Chinatown Complex!!
description: ğŸ¦€ Ultimate Singapore Chilli Crab Tour: https://youtu.be/uFbwaJ3_9iA|ğŸ”” SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/MarkWiensSubscribe Donâ€™t miss new food videos!|SINGAPORE - Welcome to Singapore and today weâ€™re going on an ultimate Singapore street food tour within the Chinatown Complex - which happens to be the biggest hawker centre in Singapore - to eat 5 of the best dishes!|Hereâ€™s the food I ate:|1. Fatty Ox HK Kitchen (https://goo.gl/maps/wRKwNDpx5RATae9S7) - This is something I was excited to try, since I love brisket egg noodles, Hong Kong style. The noodles were springy and tasty, and the beef and tendon was melt in your mouth tender. Price - S$4|2. Ma Li Ya Virgin Chicken (https://goo.gl/maps/oyQcCEPXGpZfkb9N7) - Chinatown Complex in Singapore is famous for soya sauce braised chicken, and there are two especially famous places, Hawker Chan and Ma Li Ya Virgin Chicken. I decided to go to the latter, and I was glad I did. The chicken was moist and silky all the way to the bone, and the soya sauce was delicious and comforting. I had the extra big plate with bean sprouts and silken tofu on the side. Price - S$6|3. Herbal Soup (https://goo.gl/maps/LZLaPnWusdN7PJBf7) - This was an unplanned dish of this Singapore food tour - herbal black chicken soup. I noticed it was very popular and I loved how they still cook in huge earthenware clay jars using charcoal and serve a variety of Chinese herbal soups. I ordered the black chicken herbal soup that was served with rice and tea on the side. I was delicious. Price - S$5.50|4. Zhong Guo La Mian Xiao Long Bao (https://goo.gl/maps/4r6DKTpf3N4Cax1aA) - Next up on this street food tour in Singapore, Zhong Guo La Mian Xiao Long Bao, without a doubt, one of the highlights for me. They made everything by hand. Their xiao long bao was excellent, their Sichuan spicy noodles were delicious and peanutty, but the best was their spicy wantons.  Total price - S$17|Jin Ji Teochew Braised Duck (https://goo.gl/maps/CXxN32xJvNnExF6eA) - While I was eating my dumplings, I met Melvin who owns Jin Ji Teochew Braised Duck. His braised duck place is delicious.|5. Zhao Ji Claypot Rice (https://goo.gl/maps/s4p4WJ544m1dEq516) - Finally to end this Singapore street food tour, I had to try claypot rice. Zhao Ji Claypot Rice is run by Dung, who is an extremely friendly lady. She allowed me into the kitchen to see the process. She cooks within iron pans. I ordered the extra large $28 size, though there are smaller sizes as well. She was so cool to demonstrate the entire claypot rice cooking method, mixing in a bit of oil and dark soy sauce to serve. It was the best comfort food to end an amazing day. Price - S$28|That completes this Singapore street food tour, hope you enjoyed the amazing food!|ğŸµMUSIC: |https://goo.gl/HwVjdo|â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”â€”|ğŸ“±FOLLOW:|Instagram: https://instagram.com/migrationology|Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/migrationology

title: At BRICS summit, PM Modi, Xi & Putinâ€™s first meet amid Ukraine war; Whatâ€™s on agenda?
description: Prime Minister Narendra Modi is set to attend the 14th BRICS summit to be hosted virtually this year by Chinese President XI Jinping. China is the chair of the meeting this year and will host the BRICS nations - Brazil, Russia, India and South Africa on June 23. As per reports, the meeting may not bring much to the table for India given the ongoing tension over the LAC between India and China. Xi Jinping will deliver a keynote address at the opening session of the summit on June 22 and will chair the High-level Dialogue on Global Development in Beijing on June 24. Watch this video to find out what's on the agenda of these five nations at the summit.|#india #china #russia #bricssummit #brazil #brics #southafrica #lacstandoff #ukrainerussiawar #narendramodi #xijinping #vladimirputin #ukrainewar #ukraine

title: Russia TV airs videos of Americans captured by Putinâ€™s troops; 'Don't go to Ukraine,' says Biden
description: A Russian state TV broadcaster has aired interviews with 2 captured Americans, which Russia initially refused to acknowledge. The 2 U.S. military veterans had gone missing last week in Ukraine, The latest interviews by RT claim that they have been captured by Russian troops. The U.S. military veterans - Alexander Dreuke and Andy Hyunh, can be spotted in army fatigues, speaking in Russian language. Andy Hyunh told the interviewer that the two had been hiding from Russian forces for hours in Ukraine's Kharkiv before surrendering. Meanwhile, U.S. President Joe Biden claimed that the country had no information about the whereabouts of the two Americans and urged all to not travel to Ukraine right now. Watch this video for more details.|#russia #ukraine #american #rt #vladimirputin #joebiden #kharkiv  #ukrainewar #america #ukrainerussiawar #usa #russiaukrainewar #us #russiaukraineconflict

title: Sri Lankan Black Chicken Curry | Spicy Chicken Curry | Sri Lankan Delicacy | Chicken Recipe By Varun
description: Sri Lankan Black Chicken Curry | How To Make Sri Lankan Black Chicken Curry | Chicken Kalupol Curry | Spicy Chicken Curry | Sri Lankan Chicken Curry | Sri Lankan Cuisine | How To Make Chicken Curry | Dark Chicken Curry | Chicken Curry Sri Lankan Style | Easy Chicken Curry | Chicken Gravy | Chicken Masala | Non Veg Recipe | Dinner Recipes | Chicken Curry Recipe | Chicken Recipe | Curry Recipe | Get Curried | The Bombay Chef | Varun Inamdar|Learn how to make Sri Lankan Black Chicken Curry with our Chef Varun Inamdar.|0:00 - Introduction |Sri Lankan Black Chicken Curry is one of the most popular Sri Lankan curries. It's spicy and so flavourful. Using pepper as the key ingredient and Sri Lankan curry powders, hereâ€™s how you make a delicious pepper chicken curry with coconut milk. The fresh ground pepper gives this dish a unique flavour. Black pepper is known for its health benefits, especially when it comes to digestion and antibacterial quality. If you are serving a Sri Lankan menu for lunch, you can definitely make this coconut milk-based curry. It can be served with parathas, roti, chapati, or rice. Do try this delicious chicken curry recipe today and let us know how you like it.|00:44- Chef's Trivia|01:07- Marinating the Chicken|1 kg Chicken|2 tbsp Oil|Salt (as required)|1 tbsp Ginger-Garlic Paste|2 tbsp Dark Soy Sauce|1:56- Cooking The Curry|2 tbsp Ghee|1 tsp Mustard Seeds|1 tsp Cumin Seeds|1-inch Cinnamon Stick|3 Cloves|5 Green Cardamom Pods (crushed)|10-12 Curry Leaves|1 cup Onion (sliced)|3 Green Chillies|2 Bay Leaves|1 tbsp Red Chilli Powder|1/4 tsp Turmeric Powder|1 tsp Coriander Seed Powder|2 tbsp Black Pepper (finely ground)|1 & 1/2 cup Coconut Milk|2 Banana Peppers (chopped)|1 Tomato (quartered)|#SriLankanBlackChickenCurry #CurryRecipe #GetCurried #TheBombayChef #VarunInamdar |Download the Get Curried App by clicking on this link:- http://bit.ly/GetCurriedVegNonVegRecipes_And |Host: Varun Inamdar |Copyrights: REPL |Subscribe and Get regular Updates: http://bit.ly/SubscribeToGetCurried |https://www.facebook.com/GetCurried |https://twitter.com/Get_Curried |https://instagram.com/getcurried|About Sri Lankan Cuisine|Sri Lankan food offers a vivid array of flavor combinations: sweet caramelized onion relishes, bitter melon, spicy scraped coconut, and the burn of curry tamed by mild rice, and palm sugar sweetened desserts. Samosas and dhal (lentil curry) look familiar, but upon closer inspection, these, too, have a definitively Sri Lankan spin: these thinner curries tend to be more heavily spiced than many Indian versions, and the cuisine is more inclusive of non-native ingredients, brought by international trade moving through the island. Foods that seemed to be known territory find exciting new applications in Sri Lanka, where noodles come in pancake form and pancakes serve as both bowl and base of the feast.|Sri Lankan food is not for the timid eater: the fiery curries, sweet caramelized onion in seeni sambal (onion relish), and sour lime pickle are all dominant, powerful flavors that startle awake senses dulled by the thick, hot island air. Rice is an ever-present antidote to these big flavors. A meal in Sri Lanka is called "rice and curry"â€”a term that's almost synonymous with food in general. There's rice, of course, and usually a curry with a thin broth and large chunks of the featured protein (beef, pork, fish, goat, and on from there), plus an assortment of side dishesâ€”anywhere from four to nine or ten, depending on the time and place. For a quicker bite, there are "short eats," a Sri Lankan term essentially denoting snacksâ€”often a coconut roti with hot sauce, a newspaper cone of fried spiced chickpeas, or maybe a samosa.|75% of Sri Lankans are Sinhalese (mostly Buddhist), and the food generally described as Sri Lankan is their food. Tamils (mostly Hindus), especially those in the north, use slightly different spices and other ingredients in their curries, but the format of the dishes is similar to food found on the rest of the island. Many Westerners' only reference to Tamil culture is the Tamil Tigers, a group of militant separatists from the north.|For feedback and suggestions please write to us at: foodcurry47@gmail.com

title: Ganjar Pranowo Masuk Bursa Capres Usungan NasDem, Begini Tanggapan PDIP
description: KOMPAS.TV - Ketua DPP PDI Perjuangan Puan Maharani tidak menutup peluang untuk berkoalisi dengan partai politik manapun termasuk NasDem setelah salah satu kadernya Ganjar Pranowo masuk bursa calon presiden usungan NasDem.||||Baca Juga Ini Alasan NasDem Pilih Ganjar, Anies, dan Andika Perkasa sebagai Kandidat Capres di https://www.kompas.tv/article/300286/ini-alasan-nasdem-pilih-ganjar-anies-dan-andika-perkasa-sebagai-kandidat-capres||||Puan menyebut partainya masih punya waktu satu setengah tahun untuk mematangkan strategi koalisi.||||Saat menggelar acara di sekolah Partai PDIP Lenteng Agung, Puan Maharani menegaskan membangun bangsa tidak bisa dilakukan sendiri.||||Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan hanya tersenyum dan berikan jari jempol saat dikonfirmasi terkait namanya yang paling banyak direkomendasikan oleh DPW NasDem bakal calon presiden.||||Anies tak banyak memberikan komentar usai hadiri acara di kawasan Cempaka Putih, Jakarta Pusat, Jumat siang.||||Respon berbeda diberikan Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo yang namanya juga masuk dalam kandidat bakal calon presiden yang diusung NasDem.||||Ganjar menghormati keputusan rakernas NasDem walau dengan tegas menyatakan dirinya tetap di PDIP dan menyerahkan keputusan calon presiden kepada Ketua Umum PDIP Megawati Soekarnoputri.||||Sementara Wali Kota Solo Gibran Rakabuming menegaskan hingga saat ini tidak berencana untuk maju pada Pilkada Jakarta tahun 2024 mendatang.||||Sebelumnya. Sekjen PDIP Hasto Kristiyanto mengatakan Wali Kota Solo Gibran Rakabuming Raka harus membangun hal baik bagi daerah yang dipimpinya dengan menunjukan kepemimpinan sebelum maju pilkada DKI Jakarta.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300426/ganjar-pranowo-masuk-bursa-capres-usungan-nasdem-begini-tanggapan-pdip

title: Pertemuan Acara Alumni Ansor di Surabaya Ricuh, Menag: Itu Ilegal
description: KOMPAS.TV - Menteri Agama sekaligus Ketua Umum GP Ansor Yaqut Cholil Qoumas menegaskan acara silaturahmi halal bihalal dan deklarasi Ikatan Alumni GP Ansor di Surabaya yang berujung ricuh adalah ilegal.||||Yaqut Cholil Quomas menyebut, jika Ansor merupakan organisasi kader yang memiliki struktur organisasi yang jelas.||||Baca Juga Ketua GP Ansor Luthfi Thomafi Meninggal Dunia, Gus Mus Tulis Pesan Menyentuh di https://www.kompas.tv/article/297220/ketua-gp-ansor-luthfi-thomafi-meninggal-dunia-gus-mus-tulis-pesan-menyentuh||||Sehingga jika sudah keluar dari Ansor harusnya maka menjadi anggota Nahdlatul Ulama.||||Seperti yang dilansir dari Kompas.com, kelompok pengurus GP Ansor tiba-tiba mendatangi lokasi acara tersebut dan berteriak agar acara dibubarkan.||||Sempat terjadi saling dorong antarkedua kelompok, tetapi tidak sampai terjadi baku hantam.|||| Pengurus GP Ansor aktif juga sempat meminta undangan yang mengenakan atribut Ansor untuk dilepas karena logonya telah dimodifikasi sedemikian rupa.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300423/pertemuan-acara-alumni-ansor-di-surabaya-ricuh-menag-itu-ilegal

description: Belarusian President Alexander Lukashenko has warned Kyiv against attacking Russian cities. Lukashenko claims that Zelensky is asking for long-range weapons to attack Russian cities near its border. Lukashenko added that Russia will use â€œbrand-newâ€ weapons against Ukraine if it plans to attack Russian cities. title: Kronologi Perempuan Ganggu Imam Salat di Palopo Beredar Viral, Ternyata ODGJ
description: PALOPO, KOMPAS.TV  Seorang perempuan berlari masuk ke masjid dan hendak mengganggu imam saat salat berlangsung.||||Aksi perempuan ini terekam kamera pemantau di Masjid Al-mMubarokah di Kompleks terminal dange rakko, Kota Palopo, Sulawesi Selatan, Jumat (17/6/2022).||||Menurut ketua pengurus masjid yang juga anggota Polres Palopo Aiptu Ruslan mengatakan kejadian tersebut pada saat memasuki rakaat kedua salat Jumat.||||Namun tiba-tiba masuk perempuan yang hendak mengganggu imam masjid.||||Baca Juga Viral Pria Bergelantung di Truk Tangki Pertamina, ODGJ dan Telah Diamankan ke Dinas Sosial di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298996/viral-pria-bergelantung-di-truk-tangki-pertamina-odgj-dan-telah-diamankan-ke-dinas-sosial||||"Kejadian pas kita salat jumat berjamaah ada wanita masuk ke masjid lewat pintu alternatif, langsung mau menyentuh imam masjid kita. Alhamdulillah dengan kesigapan dengan koordianator keamanan langsung mengamankan pelaku ke ruang azan. Pelaku ini warga yang memiliki kelainan,"kata Aiptu Ruslan. ||||Belakangan baru diketahui wanita 24 tahun itu ternyata orang dalam gangguan jiwa (ODGJ) yang diduga kabur dari RS Dadi Makassar. ||||Akhirnya warga yang juga mengenal wanita tersebut pun menghubungi keluarganya dan dijemput langsung oleh suaminya untuk dibawa pulang.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300355/kronologi-perempuan-ganggu-imam-salat-di-palopo-beredar-viral-ternyata-odgj

title: Yan Josua - Pesan Rindu (Official Music Video)
description: #YanJosua #PesanRindu #DADEntertainment|Judika bersama label miliknya kembali memproduseri penyanyi pria berbakat berdarah Ternate, Ambon bernama lengkap IYAN YOSUA SARUNI NANERE yang kini dikenal dengan nama YAN JOSUA. Penyanyi kelahiran Dobo, Maluku Tenggara 16 Maret 1998 ini, berhasil mencuri perhatian banyak orang termasuk Judika ketika menyanyikan lagu Judika â€œBagaimana Kalau Aku Tidak Baik-Baik Sajaâ€ pada saat mengikuti audisi di ajang pencarian bakat X Factor Indonesia 2022 yang baru saja berakhir.|Kemampuan bernyanyi Yan Josua sudah terlihat sejak umur 8 tahun. Kecintaannya akan dunia tarik suara telah membawanya menjuarai beberapa ajang pencarian bakat dari tingkat daerah sampai nasional, diantaranya Bintang RRI (2017) di Merauke, Result Show and Reunion Night Stuvo (2019) di Makasar, dan Star Voices Season 7 tahun (2021)|Nama Yan Josua pun sempat menjadi perbincangan netizen beberapa waktu lalu. Pemuda asal Merauke itu berhasil mencuri perhatian diÂ closing ceremony di Pon XX/2021Â Papua. Saat ini, Yan Josua telah merampungkan single terbarunya dengan judul â€œPesan Rinduâ€.  Lagu ciptaan nya sendiri yang ditulisnya di bangku SMA mengisahkan tentang dua insan yang saling jatuh hati dan menanyakan kabar. Demi meraih cita-cita, mereka harus berpisah dan menjalani Long Distance Relationship (LDR). Saat malam datang, kerinduan yang dalam pun tidak cukup tersampaikan lewat suara. Namun mereka percaya walaupun terpisah ruang dan waktu, tetapi sebenarnya mereka sedang memandang bulan yang sama dan berharap angin juga menyampaikan pesan rindu tersebut.|Â |â€œLagu ini sebenarnya adalah percakapan antara aku dengan seseorang lewat telepon. Aku suka nanya â€œkamu rindu gak?â€ Dan waktu itu kakak-kakak aku juga pacaran sama tentara dan â€œLDRâ€, setiap hari telponan, jadi inspirasi juga buat lagu ini.. Jadi lagu ini ditulis seperti percakapan gitu, â€œAku rindu, apakah kamu juga?â€ Aku lagi ngobrol gitu sama dia, aku rindu. Kamu juga gak? Sampe suatu ketika aku tulis seperti puisi dan jadilah lirik lagu,â€ Ujar Yan.|Â |Tidak tanggung-tanggung di single perdana nya, Dua Anak Deo (DAD) yang menjadi label dan management  tempatnya bernaung saat ini mengajak nama-nama besar untuk merampungkan lagu dan video klip â€œPESAN RINDUâ€ Yan Josua sebut saja seperti Judika, Ray Antono, Rayen Pono, Alden Luhukay dan Luthfi Aulia (Sutradara).|Â |Keinginan Yan Josua untuk menjadi seorang penyanyi terbentur dengan keinginan ayahnya yang ingin menjadikan Yan seorang tentara. â€œAku pernah memberontak keinginan ayahku karena aku gak mau jadi tentara. Saat aku lulus SMA, papa berniat masukan aku ke tentara. Aku pilih kabur, papa ku sudah panggil seorang kapten buat mendidik & melatih aku. Rambut ku sudah dipotong, semua sudah disiapkan, tapi aku lari. Untuk jadi penyanyi ini lebih ke memberontak dan mengikuti pilihan ku,â€ ungkap mahasiswa STIE Indonesia Makassar, jurusan Manajemen yang tahun ini akan wisuda.|Â |â€œSemoga single ini bisa booming, bisa menjadi berkah untuk orang-orang sekitar, bisa relate dengan orang-orang yang merasakan rindu dan bisa membahagiakan mama yang selama ini mendukung Yan jadi penyanyi, katanya.|Song Credit Â |Title : Pesan Rindu|Artist : Yan Josua|Composer : Yan Josua|Lyric : Yan Josua|Arranger : Rayen Pono & Alden Luhukay|Mixing Mastering : Alden Luhukay|Genre : Pop|Label : DAD International|Music Video Credit|Music Artist : Yan Josua|Cast Talent : Yan Josua, Balqis Carolien|Produser  : Mulya Rhukmana |Unit Produksi  : Once & Bowo|Director & Writer : Luthfi Aulia |1st Director Assistant : Frederica Vilonia |Director Of Photography : Fardan Fantasion |1st Camera Assistant  : Wahyu Imaduddin|Art Director : R. title: Paul McCartney's Relationship With The Royals
description: Paul McCartney turns 80 today, and to celebrate the event, weâ€™re looking back at the time this pop Royalty has spent with the Royal Family. |The Royal Variety Show in 1963 kicked off a decades-long relationship, as the Beatles met the Queen Mother. Only three years later, the Beatles received MBEs the Queen Elizabeth the second.|In 1996, McCartney invited the Queen to his home city - Liverpool - to formally open his performing arts school. |During this visit the Beatle refused to speak about the possibility of his knighthood. But, the highest accolade came just one year later. |It was 2002 when the singer songwriter performed the shortest Beatles number on record - Her Majesty - to the Queen at her Golden Jubilee Party At The Palace, in the grounds of Buckingham Palace. |Later that year, the Queen visited Liverpoolâ€™s Walker Art Gallery to view McCartneyâ€™s exhibition of paintings.|Finally, 21 years after he was knighted, this Beatle was made a Companion Of Honour at Buckingham Palace for, what the Royal Family called, "his lasting contribution to music in the UK and worldwide".|Follow us for more royal news, history, and highlights:|â™› Subscribe to our brand new show, exclusive to Snapchat - https://story.snapchat.com/p/85f481bd-09c1-45ce-acee-b20e629524eb/1380105951844352|â™› Subscribe to our YouTube channel (tap the bell icon and stay up to date with all the latest Royal videos!) - https://bit.ly/3jNBYZ7 |â™› Find us on TikTok https://www.tiktok.com/@royalfamilychannel |â™› Follow us on Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/RoyalFamilyChannel |â™› Tweet with us! - https://twitter.com/RoyalFamilyITNP|#PaulMcCartney #Beatles #Royalty

Chinese power companies shut down multiple plants after Pakistani government failed to pay dues to the tune of 300 billion rupees. title: Panjshir fighters parade captured Taliban commander, pilots after downing helicopter | Watch
description: Panjshir resistance fighters have released the footage of a Taliban chopper that it had shot down. The National Resistance Front (NRF) posted the visuals of the downed chopper on social media. The footage shows an M17 helicopter engulfed in smoke somewhere in Panjshir mountains of northern Afghanistan. Afghan journalist Bilal Sarwary confirmed the veracity of the NRF claim of downing the Taliban chopper. The NRF also released the pictures of captured Taliban pilots and a commander who were onboard the chopper. Panjshir fighters also posted an update about the Taliban captives, saying they are all in good health. Watch the full video for more.|#taliban #panjshir #nrf #nationalresistancefront

title: KEREN! Begini Simulasi Pengamanan KTT G20 dari Serangan Teroris oleh  Prajurit Kodam IX/Udayana
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Skenario demonstrasi dari Para Prajurit Kodam IX/Udayana dilaksanakan dalam rangka simulasi pengamanan kegiatan KTT G20.||||Kegiatan digelar di Lapangan Puputan Niti Mandala Renon, Denpasar, pada Kamis (16/5/2022).||||Skenarionya Teroris berhasil menculik beberapa Delegasi untuk dijadikan tawanan dengan tujuan menggagalkan KTT G20.||||Aksi menegangkan tersebut menyita perhatian para hadirin hingga masyarakat sekitar. ||||Baca Juga BPBD Denpasar Gelar Simulasi Kesiapsiagaan Bencana Gempa Bumi Pada Ratusan Siswa SD di https://www.kompas.tv/article/292214/bpbd-denpasar-gelar-simulasi-kesiapsiagaan-bencana-gempa-bumi-pada-ratusan-siswa-sd||||Jalan keluar masuk para Teroris telah diduduki dan dikepung menggunakan Panser-panser Anoa dari Yonif Mekanis 741/GN.||||Tak hanya itu ada juga tim Jihandak Yonzipur 18/YKR menggunakan Ransus unit EOD Ivander, untuk menjinakkan bom yang ditempelkan di tubuh salah satu sandera.||||"Simulasi dan Demonstrasi ini juga sebagai bukti bahwa Kodam IX/Udayana siap mendukung Provinsi Bali sebagai tuan rumah dalam mensukseskan pelaksanaan KTT G20 mendatang," kata Pangdam.||||Pangdam IX/Udayana Mayjen TNI Sonny Aprianto pihaknya akan  secara maksimal untuk mengamankan dan mensukseskan pelaksanaan kegiatan G20.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300310/keren-begini-simulasi-pengamanan-ktt-g20-dari-serangan-teroris-oleh-prajurit-kodam-ix-udayana

title: Park Hyung-sik dives into a mob of zombies to save Han Hyo-joo | Happiness Ep 3 [ENG SUB]

title: Nikita Mirzani Jadi Tersangka? Ini Klarifikasi Polresta Serang Kota
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV Kepolisian Polresta Serang memberikan klarifikasi terkait beredarnya surat penetapan tersangka atas nama Nikita Mirzani. ||||Bantahan ini disampaikan oleh Plt Wakapolresta Serang Kota AKBP Wahyu Imam, Jumat (17/6/2022).||||"Yang pertama, kami memonitor adanya dokumen beredar di media sosial tentang status Saudari NM sebagai tersangka. Maka kami menjawab bahwa Saudara NM belum kami tetapkan sebagai tersangka," kata AKBP Wahyu.||||Kepolisian Polresta Serang Kota akan memonitor adanya dokumen yang beredar viral di media sosial itu. ||||Baca Juga Rumah Nikita Mirzani di Pesanggrahan Jakarta Selatan Didatangi Polisi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/299505/rumah-nikita-mirzani-di-pesanggrahan-jakarta-selatan-didatangi-polisi||||"Kedua, walaupun adanya kebocoran dokumen tersebut, akan kami lakukan penyelidikan dan penyidikan tersebut," ujarnya singkat.||||Sebelumnya, Nikita Mirzani membantah status tersebut. ||||Persoalan pelaporan Nikita ke Polres Serang dilakukan oleh Dito Mahendra atas dugaan tindak pidana penghinaan, pencemaran nama baik melalui sarana ITE. ||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300306/nikita-mirzani-jadi-tersangka-ini-klarifikasi-polresta-serang-kota

title: Acungan Jempol Anies Usai Namanya Masuk Bakal Capres Nasdem
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Partai NasDem telah mengumumkan tiga nama bakal capres untuk Pilpres 2024 di antaranya ada Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan, Panglima TNI Jenderal Andika Perkasa dan Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo. ||||Anies Baswedan saat ditanya media terkait namanya masuk bursa bakal capres Nasdem tidak berkomentar. ||||Anies hanya mengacungkan jempolnya ke arah kamera.||||Baca Juga Ini 3 Nama Diusulkan Nasdem jadi Capres 2024: Anies, Andika Perkasa, Ganjar di https://www.kompas.tv/article/300232/ini-3-nama-diusulkan-nasdem-jadi-capres-2024-anies-andika-perkasa-ganjar||||Momen tersebut dilakukan oleh Gubernur DKI Jakarta Anies Baswedan usai hadiri acara di kawasan Cempaka ||Putih, Jakarta Pusat, Jumat (17/6/2022). ||||Sebelumnya tiga nama itu diumumkan oleh Ketua Umum Surya Paloh di Rakernas NasDem, JCC, Senayan, Jakarta, Jumat (17/6/2022). ||||Bukan tanpa alasan 3 nama bakal capres tersebut adalah hasil usulan seluruh DPW NasDem yang dilanjutkan dalam musyawarah steering committee.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300291/acungan-jempol-anies-usai-namanya-masuk-bakal-capres-nasdem
tags: andika perkasa|anies baswedan|capres 2024|ganjar pranowo|nasdem|pdip|surya paloh

title: Disney worker among arrests in Florida child predator sting: full press conference
description: An undercover online child predator investigation resulted in the arrest of a dozen suspects in Polk County, according to investigators with the Polk County Sheriff's Office, Auburndale Police Department, and Winter Haven Police Department, who worked together on "Operation Child Protector II." Sheriff Grady Judd said 12 suspects were arrested for a total of 49 felonies, and nine of the 12 had no criminal history. Four of the suspects allegedly traveled to an undercover location to meet someone they thought was a teenage girl, between the ages of 13 and 15, but instead found detectives waiting to arrest them. The strike on a cultural center killed a mother and daughter, as well as a young man and a bedridden woman who had moved there to shelter from her home in Severodonetsk.|The bombing on Thursday sparked a fire that raged through Stalin-era Diamant Palace of Culture overnight and was still burning on Friday. Police said that around 10 people were injured, some seriously after being trapped by debris. Meanwhile, a key highway out of Lysychansk is now impassable due to Russian shelling, Luhansk regional governor Serhiy Gaidai said in an online post on Friday.|Serhiy Haidai, the governor of the eastern Ukrainian region of Luhansk, said that there are 568 people sheltering in the Azot chemical plant in the city of Sievierodonetsk, where fighting has been raging. "Exit from the plant is possible only with a complete cease-fire."|German Chancellor Olaf  Scholz has insisted that German weapons will arrive in time to help Ukraine fend off Russian forces in the eastern Donbas region. His comments, in an exclusive interview with DPA news agency, come amid criticism from Kyiv over the pace of weapons deliveries and the type of weapons sent.|Asked whether the heavy weaponry will arrive in time to make a difference in the Donbas, Scholz answered: "It will arrive in time." He said the priority for who gets German weapons first had to be changed as German arms manufacturers have a "long list of customers" waiting for deliveries. The chancellor promised to deliver an anti-ballistic missile system that is able to protect Odesa or Kyiv and said Berlin had decided together with the UK and the United States that it will deliver multiple rocket launchers.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Ukraine #Russia #EU

title: Bodycam Video Shows LAPD SWAT Shoot Alleged Armed Suspect During Standoff
description: The Los Angeles Police Department released bodycam video showing their SWAT team shooting an allegedly armed suspect, 54-year-old Leron James, on May 3. Central Patrol officers responded to a backup request from the Los Angeles Fire Department about a suicidal man. Upon arrival, the man pointed a gun at officers after they tried to speak to him, prompting officers to request additional backup from the LAPD SWAT team and the Crisis Negotiation team. The SWAT team used a chemical agent in an attempt to coerce the suspect out of his apartment. The suspect responded by shooting his firearm out his window, at which time an officer shot him. Officers pronounced the suspect deceased at the scene. description: Prime Time With Ravish Kumar - June 17, 2022: Protests against the Centre's 'Agnipath' recruitment scheme for the Armed forces took a serious turn in Bihar where trains were torched and railway properties vandalised. title: Starship Troopers: Terran Command Review
description: Starship Troopers: Terran Command reviewed by Leana Hafer on PC.||||Starship Troopers: Terran Command has the exoskeleton of a strong RTS with some unique, asymmetrical, positioning-focused warfare. There are just a handful of hitches that keep it from being really great. A campaign that takes too long to become challenging, some frustratingly bad pathfinding and targeting AI, and the lack of multiplayer or a scenario editor are the main ones. But if all you're looking for is a competent single-player campaign that hits all the notes I'd expect as a Starship Troopers fan, and eventually provides some diverse and challenging tactical puzzles to solve, you'll find it here.|#IGN #Gaming

title: Menggembirakan, Indonesia Memiliki Tingkat Produktivitas Gabah ke 2 di Asia Tenggara

title: The Callisto Protocol Reveal Destroys IGNâ€™s Summer of Gaming 2022
description: The Callisto Protocol invaded IGN's Summer of Gaming and it definitely was not a safe place for anyone here in the studio, and all the chaos was sponsored by The Callisto Protocol.||||The Callisto Protocol is a a third-person sci-fi horror survival  game developed by Striking Distance Studios and was founded by Dead Space creator Glen Schofield. ||You play as Jacob Lee, voiced by Josh Duhamel, who is a prisoner on the moon trying to survive during a "mysterious outbreak" that's mutating people into terrible monsters called Biophage. Schofield says "horror starts with atmosphere," and that special antention has been paid to things like lighting and the PS5's 3D audio. The Callisto Protocol will also take advantage of The Dualsense controller's haptics for everything from heavy enemy footsteps to swinging your weapon. ||||The Callisto Protocol realease December 2, 2022 on Xbox One, Playstation 4, Playstation 5 (PS5), Xbox Series X|S, and PC.|#IGN #IGNSummerOfGaming

title: VISITING DDE HQ! Damon's Porsche Carrera GT MAKEOVER in Signal Green
description: It's 'Signal Green' Porsche Carrera GT time! @DailyDrivenExotics have remodelled their HQ in LA, and now given the CGT a new look too. Let's check it out at PFS before heading over to the garage to check out what's going on. That V10 is a masterpiece, and who needs tires anyway...|Damon bought the iconic Porsche supercar a year ago, originally in Seal Grey over Terracotta, but has now taken it to @Protective Film Solutions for an all new look in a wrap like Porsche's PTS Signal Green. After meeting up and taking a look at the changes including the new AL13 wheels and gloss black elements around the car, it's time for a catch up and drive out on the road to head to DDE HQ.|It wasn't that long ago that Damon and Dave got the keys to their shop, although while they've been away on @Gumball 3000, the whole place has had an extensive remodelling; from the floor to walls and the new lighting that's just been installed. At the moment it features 3 generations of Lamborghini V12; Aventador SVJ, Murcielago LP640 and Diablo SV, plus the Ferrari 550 Maranello project build, and a few of the Viper drift cars amongst others.|Inspired by Fast and the Furious, the DDE HQ features a storage area, working area, team kitchen and offices, and will be home to many of their ongoing projects. Oh, and there turn out to be some fairly random items around too... title: WATCH: Why Mike Pence refused to leave the Capitol on Jan. 6 #shorts
description: During the Jan. 6 committee hearing on June 16, Greg Jacob, the chief counsel to former Vice President Mike Pence, said Pence refused to leave the U.S. Capitol as rioters breached the building on Jan. 6, 2021.|Pence had been moved to a secured location as rioters moved through the building. At one point, the head of his Secret Service detail asked him to get into a car for his safety. Pence refused, saying he did not want to risk the car leaving with him in it.| "The vice president did not want to take any chance that the world would see the vice president of the United States, fleeing the United States Capitol," Jacob said.|Jacob added that Pence was "determined" to certify the votes and did not want to give the rioters the "satisfaction" of further delaying or stopping the count.|The committee presented new evidence about the danger Pence faced  as former President Donald Trump sent out a tweet criticizing the vice president. As rioters at the Capitol focused their anger on the vice president, they at one point came within 40 feet of Pence within the building.|Stream your PBS favorites with the PBS app: https://to.pbs.org/2Jb8twG|Find more from PBS NewsHour at https://www.pbs.org/newshour|Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://bit.ly/2HfsCD6|Follow us:|TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@pbsnews|Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/newshour|Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/newshour|Facebook: http://www.pbs.org/newshour|Subscribe:|PBS NewsHour podcasts: https://www.pbs.org/newshour/podcasts|Newsletters: https://www.pbs.org/newshour/subscribe

title: Russia captures two American military veterans in Ukraine; Biden admin urges 'humane treatment'
description: The United States on Thursday urged Russia to treat any American volunteers captured while fighting alongside Ukrainian troops as prisoners of war guaranteed humane treatment. The State Department also said that a third American was believed to be missing in Ukraine in addition to two military veterans who were reportedly seized by Russian forces in a pitched battle last week. Families and members of Congress said Wednesday that Alexander Drueke and Andy Huynh, both US military veterans who had been living in Alabama, lost contact with their relatives last week while fighting with Ukrainian forces near the Russian border.|#Russia #Ukraine #russiaukraineconflict #russiaukrainewar #ukrainecrisis #vladimirputin #putin #joebiden #america #nedprice

title: 192 Kepala Daerah dari PDI-P Ikuti Sekolah Partai, Ganjar Hadir Usai Disebut Kemlinthi
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Ratusan kepala daerah yang merupakan kader PDI Perjuangan, berolahraga bersama pada hari terakhir sekolah partai di Lenteng Agung, Jakarta Selatan.||||Tampak di antara kepala daerah yang mengikuti senam bersama, Wali Kota Solo Gibran Rakabuming Raka, Wali Kota Medan yang juga ipar Gibran, Bobby Nasution, dan Gubernur Jawa Tengah, Ganjar Pranowo. selain itu tampak pula Sekjen PDI Perjuangan, Hasto Kristiyanto.||||Kemunculan Ganjar Pranowo dalam acara sekolah partai di Lenteng Agung, mengundang perhatian. ||||Sebab belakangan sejumlah politisi PDIP kerap mengritik Ganjar yang dianggap terlalu berambisi maju dalam Pilpres 2024. ||||Baca Juga Partai Nasdem Usulkan 3 Nama Capres, Anies dan Ganjar Paling Banyak Dipilih di https://www.kompas.tv/article/300203/partai-nasdem-usulkan-3-nama-capres-anies-dan-ganjar-paling-banyak-dipilih||||Dalam unggahan di akun instagramnya, Gubernur Jawa Tengah Ganjar Pranowo menunjukkan bangsal yang ia tinggali, selama mengikuti sekolah partai bersama para kepala daerah dari PDI Perjuangan.||||Mess tempat Ganjar menginap, berisi sejumlah tempat tidur bertingkat dan lemari kecil. ||||Selama acara berlangsung, para kepala daerah menginap bersama tanpa didampingi ajudan masing-masing.||||192 kepala daerah dari PDI - Perjuangan, mengikuti rapat konsolidasi kepala daerah di sekolah partai selama dua hari, yang berakhir hari ini.||||Rapat koordinasi ini diadakan sebagai persiapan menghadapi pemilu 2024. ||||Para kepala daerah mendapatkan sejumlah pembekalan, salah satunya dari Menteri Keuangan Sri Mulyani.|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/300228/192-kepala-daerah-dari-pdi-p-ikuti-sekolah-partai-ganjar-hadir-usai-disebut-kemlinthi

title: Nupur Sharma missing? Mumbai cops hunt for 'untraceable' suspended BJP leader over Prophet row
description: Former BJP spokesperson Nupur Sharma, who sparked fury in India and among Islamic nations with her remarks on the Prophet, is missing. Mumbai police have said that she is untraceable for 4 days now. This comes just 8 days ahead of her appearance before Mumbai police, to record a statement in connection to a FIR filed against her. The case was filed on May 29 following a complaint by Irfan Shaikh, the joint secretary of Mumbai wing of Raza Academy. Nupur Sharma was booked on charges of hurting religious feelings, promoting enmity and causing public mischief. title: â€˜Riverdaleâ€™ Actor Pleads Guilty to Killing His Mom
description: A child star is facing serious allegations. Ryan Grantham, who appeared in the movie "Diary of a Wimpy Kid" and the hit TV series "Riverdale," pled guilty to killing his own mother in British Columbia, Canada. The actor also allegedly had plans to assassinate Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau. The day after allegedly murdering his mother, he loaded his car with three guns, ammunition, 12 Molotov cocktails and a map to where the prime minister and his family live.

title: Escaping Brazil's Deadliest Gangs
